 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uaerimusshadowborn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aerimus Shadowborn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/15/01 2:23:57 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=325.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: best 2 person combo?</span><hr size=1> Dunno about the 2 wizard thing wizards can go down fast I think enc + shaman personally any pair no matter what if tash takes em down to the point where malo can stick they will be done. Tash malo mez one wizard kill the other then move on to the next. Also there is the slight issue of people gating or fleeing. People who with mr knocked down to nil will have a harder time running. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukambic.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kambic</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/15/01 3:06:51 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=325.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.theglobe.com/Kambic/TRINITY.GIF WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: best 2 person combo?</span><hr size=1> Well, 2 wizards is still the best for quick raw damage. I'm talking about situations where they are not expecting it, you walk in invis, the pair of you unload two nukes, loot the corpse and walk away, and the guy's group didn't even know he died yet. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=cylant>Cylant</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/15/01 1:08:58 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=325.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: best 2 person combo?</span><hr size=1> The most lethal pvp combo i ever saw was a 55 wizard and a 55 enchanter(unresistable mez).  They had it timed so that by the time ice comet landed, you had .2 seconds to be un-mezzed =P.  This would work really well on the new server also - since nobody has enough MR to deal with tash. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukambic.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kambic</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/15/01 6:08:13 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=325.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.theglobe.com/Kambic/TRINITY.GIF WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: best 2 person combo?</span><hr size=1> Aye, and probably what me and a friend are going to do if I stick with chanter ;p<br>
